Project Supervisors Complete Training in Tianjin
TIANJIN , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- China 's first group of 60 supervisors for key State projects graduated from a four-month training program at Tianjin University here today .
The supervisors , from the State Development Planning Commission , will be sent to posts nationwide in January to strengthen the supervision of the country 's major investment and construction projects .
The 60 completed a variety of supervision courses including assessment and bidding for construction projects , administration of contracts , quality control and security management , financial systems , and engineering costs and related laws .
